---
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
	<title>Adult Family Home - Kirkland, WA</title>
	<style>
		* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
		body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
		header { background-color: #2D5016; color: white; padding: 1rem 0; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
		.header-content { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
		.logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; }
		nav a { color: white; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 2rem; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
		nav a:hover { opacity: 0.8; }
		.hero { background: linear-gradient(rgba(45, 80, 22, 0.7), rgba(45, 80, 22, 0.7)), url(/images/1.png); background-size: cover; background-position: center; color: white; padding: 6rem 20px; text-align: center; min-height: 500px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
		.hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
		.hero p { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
		.hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
		.btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; transition: background-color 0.3s; }
		.btn:hover { background-color: #0052a3; }
		.btn-secondary { background-color: #1B4F72; }
		.btn-secondary:hover { background-color: #133956; }
		.container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
		.content-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
		.content-section h2 { color: #2D5016; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.8rem; }
		.content-section h3 { color: #2D5016; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.3rem; }
		.content-section p { color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
		.image-float-left { float: left; width: 28%; max-width: 220px; margin: 0 1.5rem 1rem 0; border-radius: 8px; }
		.image-float-right { float: right; width: 28%; max-width: 220px; margin: 0 0 1rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; }
		.content-section::after { content: ""; display: table; clear: both; }
		ul { margin: 1rem 0 0 1.5rem; color: #666; }
		ul li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
		.testimonials { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
		.testimonial-card { background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #2D5016; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
		.testimonial-card p { color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }
		.testimonial-author { color: #2D5016; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; }
		.highlight-box { text-align: center; background: #f0f0f0; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 2rem; }
		.highlight-box h3 { color: #2D5016; }
		.highlight-box a { color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
		.bottom-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 1rem; }
		footer { background-color: #2D5016; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
		.footer-contact { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
		.footer-contact a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<div class="header-content">
			<div class="logo">Adult Family Home</div>
			<nav>
				<a href="/">Home</a>
				<a href="/about">About</a>
				<a href="/services">Services</a>
				<a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
				<a href="/news">News</a>
				<a href="/contact">Contact</a>
				<a href="/legal">Legal</a>
			</nav>
		</div>
	</header>

	<div class="hero">
		<h1>Safe, home-like living with consistent caregivers and personalized care.</h1>
		<p>A warm, family-like environment in Kirkland, Washington</p>
		<div class="hero-buttons">
			<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc6zOPC_-XkiE4FFxW-MbLW13HCLkGp7LDdFpJXXJlNcikH5Q/viewform?usp=header" class="btn" target="_blank">Schedule a Visit</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="container">
		<div class="content-section">
			<h2>Welcome to Our Adult Family Home</h2>
			<img src="/images/1.png" alt="Front exterior" class="image-float-left">
			<p>We provide personalized, compassionate care for adults who need support with daily living. Our home offers a safe, comfortable environment where residents receive individualized attention and meaningful engagement. Every detail of our home is designed with resident safety and comfort in mind.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="content-section">
			<h3>Our Approach</h3>
			<img src="/images/4.png" alt="Caregiver assisting resident" class="image-float-right">
			<p>We believe care should be delivered with dignity, respect, and warmth. Every resident is treated as a valued member of our family. Our approach centers on listening to each resident's needs and adjusting care accordingly.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="content-section">
			<h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
			<img src="/images/2.png" alt="Living room" class="image-float-left">
			<ul>
				<li>Safe, comfortable home environment with 24/7 supervision</li>
				<li>Personalized care plans tailored to individual needs</li>
				<li>Experienced, compassionate caregivers</li>
				<li>Nutritious, home-cooked meals</li>
				<li>Social engagement and meaningful activities</li>
			</ul>
			<p>We understand that choosing a care setting is one of the most important decisions a family makes.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="content-section">
			<h3>What Families Say</h3>
			<div class="testimonials">
				<div class="testimonial-card">
					<p>"My mother has thrived in this home. The care is attentive, the staff treats her like family, and I see her genuinely happy."</p>
					<div class="testimonial-author">— Harry</div>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial-card">
					<p>"The home feels warm and secure. My dad's needs are met with kindness and professionalism."</p>
					<div class="testimonial-author">— Sally</div>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial-card">
					<p>"This is the kind of place I want for my future. The residents are well cared for."</p>
					<div class="testimonial-author">— David</div>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial-card">
					<p>"We felt supported from the first phone call through admission and beyond."</p>
					<div class="testimonial-author">— Ava</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="highlight-box">
			<h3>Ready to Learn More?</h3>
			<p>Explore our <a href="/about">about us</a>, <a href="/services">services</a>, <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>, or <a href="/contact">contact us</a> today.</p>
			<div class="bottom-buttons">
				<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc6zOPC_-XkiE4FFxW-MbLW13HCLkGp7LDdFpJXXJlNcikH5Q/viewform?usp=header" class="btn" target="_blank">Schedule a Visit</a>
				<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Get in Touch</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<footer>
		<div class="footer-contact">
			<a href="tel:425-123-4567" style="color: #fff;">425-123-4567</a> | <a href="mailto:contact@afh.wamj@gmail.com" style="color: #fff;">contact@afh.wamj@gmail.com</a> | 7am–7pm, 7 days a week
		</div>
		<p>&copy; 2026 Adult Family Home. All rights reserved.</p>
		<div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
			<a href="/" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Back to Home</a>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>
